Installer code

** Installer on Mac:
> npm install electron-packager -g
> cd flow-installer
> ./build-maxosx.sh

This will build the full app into flow-installer/FlowApp-darwin-x64

** Installer on Windows
> npm install electron-packager -g
> cd flow-installer
> ./build-windows.bat

** Uploading an install:
> node upload.js
This will automagically figure out the platform, and upload the generated setup


